Reference manual p 137:

    The example should read as follows:

        (*
          This example also illustrates the use
          of ReadNextEntry
        *)

        IMPORT FIO, IO;

        VAR
          Ent : FIO.DirEntry;
          FOUND : BOOLEAN;

        BEGIN
          ...
          Found := FIO.ReadFirstEntry( "C:\COM\*.EXE",
                                       FIO.FileAttr{FIO.system,FIO.hidden},
                                       Ent);

          WHILE Found DO
             IO.WrStr(Ent.Name);
             IO.WrLn;
             Found := FIO.ReadNextEntry(Ent);
          END;
        ...

